 white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appiu7n5lWz2984/image/ueditor/91828500_1546920640.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="500548670.jpg"/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><strong style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">无忧无虑的生活，只是人类一厢情愿的幻想，苦难和挫折是人生的常态而不是意外。</span></strong></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><strong style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><strong style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appiu7n5lWz2984/image/ueditor/18424200_1546920641.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="500618062.jpg"/></span></strong></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">俗话说：「人生不如意十常八九」，所以如何面对和处理不如意，才是人生的主要课题。 更重的是，没有人可以替别人过活，<strong style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;">每一个人都必须自己活这一生，因此如何经营一个充实、有意义的幸福人生，只能靠自己。</strong></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><br/></strong></span></p><section style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; z-index: 0; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; position: relative !important;"><section style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; border: 0px none; z-index: 0; position: relative !important;"><section style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 5px auto; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; width: 384px; text-align: center;"><section style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; display: inline-block; width: auto;"><section style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; display: -webkit-flex; align-items: center;"><section style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; width: 60px;"><section style="max-inline-size: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 60px; height: 46px; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appiu7n5lWz2984/image/ueditor/83730900_1546920640.com/cache/remote/ahr0chm6ly9tbwjpei5xbg9nby5jbi9tbwjpel9wbmcvdu4xtelhdjdvsjhxazvjwmj4bjlrq0g4awj1nm81awndz2diawnaunnwwuzpylhrcmlhsje3ull0bfvpy3fhc29xr0k3sgj3wtc3chrry3g3cg16ee5xz1qxruevmd93ef9mbxq9cg5n&#39;); background-size: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"></section></section><section style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 5px 0px 0px -50px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><section style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; display: inline-block; width: auto;"><section style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><strong>怎么活比较好？</strong></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这不是别人的课题，而是<strong>每一个会思考者</strong>必须思索的问题。听完这一个系列，你应该有能力为自己的生命找到努力的方向。 &nbsp;</span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appiu7n5lWz2984/image/ueditor/42472400_1546920641.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="500608246.jpg"/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;">讲师介绍</span></strong></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><strong style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">林火旺教授</span></strong><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;生于淡水出海口的农村—关渡，美国爱荷华大学哲学博士，新生代基金会董事长。曾任民生报记者、台大课外活动组主任、台大哲学系主任兼研究所所长、政策顾问；2017年8月从台大哲学系退休，曾任实践大学讲座教授，现为台大哲学系兼任教授。&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p><section style="border: 0px none; margin: 0px auto; width: 95%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 5px;border: 5px solid #fefefe; box-shadow: #e6e6dc 1px 1px 5px 1px; border-radius: 2%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.6);"><p><img style="border-top-left-radius: 2%; border-top-right-radius: 2%; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px; height: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appiu7n5lWz2984/image/ueditor/50025100_1546920641.jpg" width="100%" height="auto" title="hwphoto02.jpg" alt="hwphoto02.jpg"/></p><section style="padding: 20px 10px;box-sizing:border-box;border-width: 5px 0px 0px; border-style: solid none none; border-left-color: #dbdbdb; border-top-color: #fefefe; border-bottom-left-radius: 2%; border-bottom-right-radius: 2%; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">林火旺，人如其名，<strong>他充满高度生命热忱和知识分子的济世心肠</strong>。</span><span style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">同时，他的名字也透露他真正来自乡土的民间社会。</span></span></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 16px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;">林火旺是台湾研究伦理学、自由主义、社会正义、多元文化、公民理论等的重要学者。但这些听起来冰冷而深奥的西洋学术殿堂的名词，经过火旺教授经年累月的揉捏，已经塑形为充满泥土温度和气味的语言。</span><br/></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appiu7n5lWz2984/image/ueditor/65853700_1546920641.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="IMG_6217.JPG"/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">火旺教授的著作《道德-幸福的必要条件》已印刷了二十几版，<strong>深受社会各阶层的喜爱和肯定</strong>。他深入各地学校、企业、医院、社区演讲，他以热情的语言、透彻的分析、渊博的知识、精彩的实例，一次又一次的和大家分享人生的价值、道德的深义，以及处于社会乱象中哲学思考的必要。 &nbsp;</span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">很多朋友听完总觉得意犹未尽，希望他能好好为生命说个道理，于是，我们规划了这一系列课程，希望大家喜欢，希望听完后，<strong>更珍爱自己的生命，也更尊重他人的生命。</strong></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="-webkit-max-logical-width: 100%; margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color:#595959"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">课程预告（滑动查看）</span></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 16px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); white-space: normal; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"></span></p><p><br/></p><section style="border: 0px none; margin: 0px auto; width: 95%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="overflow: scroll; height: 300px; width: 100%; display: inline-block; color: inherit;overflow-x: hidden;"><section style="padding: 10px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #3d5862; border-color: #a9a9a9; background-color: #c4d4da;"><section style="color: inherit; border-color: rgb(196, 212, 218); padding: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; mar